# Storyblok Demo Rules

## Overview
When asked to create a demo for storyblok, follow these rules.

## Required Workflow Steps
- Follow the cms-integration.mdc rules.
- Follow the figma.mdc rules.
- Create a demo for the component in the storyblok demo folder.
- Create a page within a /demo/[component-name]/page.tsx file. This page will be used to display the demo of the component.
- When creating a component, make sure to add the basic placeholder text for the component. But when creating a demo, fill in al the required fields for the component.